This is simple test project developed in Erlang for education purposes.

It should work on both Linux and Windows OS in development mode, release 
should work on Linux only.

PREREQUISITES
This project requires erlang installed in development PC on both Linux and 
Windows. For Windows cygwin with make should also be installed.

BUILD PROJECT
Use make(1) for build project. 

RUN PROJECT
You can run project with

/> start-dev.cmd

on Windows and 

/> start-dev.sh

on Linux.

